<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>

        <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
        <section class="bm-hero">
            <div class="bm-hero-inner">
                <h1 class="bm-hero-title">Smarter Operations Without<br>Increasing Staff</h1>
                <p class="bm-hero-subtitle">Automate daily restaurant workflows with AI and IoT—so you can serve more customers, reduce errors, and control costs without hiring more people.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bm-btn-primary">Get started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== FEATURES ===== -->
        <section class="bm-features" id="features">
            <div class="bm-features-inner">

                <div class="bm-badge">Bhojan Mitra POS</div>

                <div class="rpos-feature-list">

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Centralized, Automated Order Management</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Upgrade from manual systems to an AI-driven POS for precise order capture and direct routing to the kitchen. This minimizes errors and streamlines operations. Enhance efficiency and reduce misunderstandings with automated order processing. Focus on customer satisfaction, not order corrections.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Lower Dependency on Skilled Staff</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Intuitive voice commands and support for multiple languages empower new and seasonal employees to perform effectively. This reduces the time spent on training and alleviates staffing challenges. Our system ensures smooth operations, regardless of employee experience or language proficiency. Boost team performance and morale with tools designed for inclusivity and ease of use.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Reduce Wastage and Operational Costs</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Intelligent coordination in the kitchen is crucial for minimizing errors, reducing waste, and preventing delays, which directly translates to cost savings for restaurants on every order. Our system ensures that resources are used efficiently, and waste is minimized. This leads to improved profitability and sustainability. By optimizing kitchen processes, restaurants can achieve significant savings and enhance their bottom line.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Built for Indian Restaurant Realities</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Our system is tailored to meet the unique demands of Indian restaurants, from managing peak hours to accommodating diverse menus. It supports multiple regional languages to ensure clear communication and efficient order processing. The adaptable design integrates seamlessly into existing workflows, enhancing productivity and reducing operational friction. Experience a solution that understands and addresses the specific needs of your restaurant.</p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
        <section class="rpos-cta">
            <div class="rpos-cta-inner">
                <h2 class="rpos-cta-title">Want to Know more</h2>
                <p class="rpos-cta-sub">Join the pilot to experience voice ordering, IoT routing, and analytics tailored to your restaurant before our public launch.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bm-btn-primary">Join the program</a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js?v=<%= locals.assetVersion %>"></script>
</body>
</html>
